---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Blog" description="Expert real estate insights and market analysis for the Sunshine Coast">
  <section class="blog-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <hgroup>
        <h1>Market Insights & Blog</h1>
        <p>Expert analysis and advice from Jack McGhee</p>
      </hgroup>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid">
        <article>
          <header class="blog-image-placeholder"></header>
          <small>January 2026</small>
          <h3><a href="/blog/sunshine-coast-2026-data-driven-growth">The Sunshine Coast 2026: Data-Driven Growth for Property Investors</a></h3>
          <p>
            Current data from the Australian Bureau of Statistics and Sunshine Coast Council confirms 
            the region is outperforming national growth averages. Discover the official numbers driving 
            the market in 2026.
          </p>
          <footer><a href="/blog/sunshine-coast-2026-data-driven-growth">Read More →</a></footer>
        </article>

        <article>
          <header class="blog-image-placeholder"></header>
          <small>December 2025</small>
          <h3><a href="/blog/sunshine-coast-market-outlook-2026">The Sunshine Coast Property Market: 2026 Outlook</a></h3>
          <p>
            As we enter 2026, the Sunshine Coast continues to be one of Australia's most dynamic 
            property markets. Discover the key trends shaping the region and what they mean for 
            buyers and sellers in the year ahead.
          </p>
          <footer><a href="/blog/sunshine-coast-market-outlook-2026">Read More →</a></footer>
        </article>

        <article>
          <header class="blog-image-placeholder"></header>
          <small>November 2025</small>
          <h3><a href="/blog/first-time-buyer-tips">5 Essential Tips for First-Time Home Buyers</a></h3>
          <p>
            Navigating your first property purchase can be overwhelming, but it doesn't have to be. 
            Here's my expert advice to make your first home buying experience smooth and successful.
          </p>
          <footer><a href="/blog/first-time-buyer-tips">Read More →</a></footer>
        </article>

        <article>
          <header class="blog-image-placeholder"></header>
          <small>October 2025</small>
          <h3><a href="/blog/selling-property-sunshine-coast">Selling Your Property on the Sunshine Coast: A Strategic Guide</a></h3>
          <p>
            Learn the proven strategies that maximize property value in the Sunshine Coast market, 
            from presentation and marketing to negotiation and closing.
          </p>
          <footer><a href="/blog/selling-property-sunshine-coast">Read More →</a></footer>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    /* Page-specific styles for blog page */
    .blog-hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--ocean-deep) 0%, var(--ocean-blue) 100%);
      color: var(--white);
      padding: 4rem 0;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: -1px;
    }

    .blog-hero h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      color: var(--white);
    }

    .blog-hero p {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: var(--sand-warm);
    }

    .blog-image-placeholder {
      height: 250px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--ocean-light) 0%, var(--sand-warm) 100%);
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
    }

    article h3 a {
      color: var(--ocean-deep);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    article h3 a:hover {
      color: var(--ocean-blue);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .blog-hero h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
